-- National Grid says U.S. authority approves KeySpan bid
-- 
-- Tue Oct 24, 2006 4:36am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2006/10/24/us-energy-nationalgrid-idUSWLA491420061024

 

 LONDON  (Reuters) - Britain's National Grid Plc ( NG.L ) said on Tuesday the U.S. Federal Energy Regulatory Commission (FERC) had voted to approve its proposed acquisition of natural gas distributor KeySpan Corp. KSE.N. 

